raid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"2aca17fb6a642d6e9da7e3a87c5eed19cc73856d","tid":2087231,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"},{"pid":"54ae3b0c6497c58b94b897bcce15f242dd5ab80b","tid":2087231,"uid":14229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"由于此讯息不符合国家安全法规，已被屏蔽。"},{"pid":"692e2d02295b2e4cfa3fcdc054919c962c5db8f9","tid":2087231,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"Sogo 真特價！<br />\n<br />\n突發！Sogo 大特價，買$3000平$500！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論"}]}